      <title>日本央行利率：据称官员正在考虑三月份加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-12/boj-rates-officials-said-to-be-weighing-a-march-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，日本央行官员距离加息越来越近，并将在下周的政策会议上决定是否在本月采取行动，目前结果还很难说。彭博社的保罗·杰克逊报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-12/boj-rates-officials-said-to-be-weighing-a-march-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 07:38:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市开始见证各个行业的牛市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-stocks-begin-witnessing-bull-markets-in-a-gamut-of-sectors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国一些新旧经济领域的牛市已经开始，这表明投资者看到了习近平主席提振经济和市场的措施带来的当前估值的上升空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-stocks-begin-witnessing-bull-markets-in-a-gamut-of-sectors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 07:06:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
