      <title>新加坡采取措施让游客进出更加方便</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/singapore-moves-to-make-visitor-travel-in-and-out-even-easier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡正在让人们更加方便地往返于这个热带城邦，允许司机通过两个陆地检查站进入该国时使用二维码而不是护照。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/singapore-moves-to-make-visitor-travel-in-and-out-even-easier</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 07:05:14 GMT</pubDate>
